{
  "video_id": "uBgRo9tnv-I",
  "title": "Discussing the merits of Unconditional Basic Income | Enno Schmidt | TEDxBasel",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 22160.0,
      "end_time": 23950.0,
      "text": "HF: For those who don&#39;t know about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 23950.0,
      "end_time": 28220.0,
      "text": "can you briefly tell us what basic income is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 28220.0,
      "end_time": 33880.0,
      "text": "ES A basic income is the base of income for the basic needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 33880.0,
      "end_time": 35540.0,
      "text": "and the thought is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 35540.0,
      "end_time": 38500.0,
      "text": "that these basic needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 38500.0,
      "end_time": 44280.0,
      "text": "must not be strictly bounded to some conditions;"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 44280.0,
      "end_time": 47080.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s necessary to have it for everybody;"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 47080.0,
      "end_time": 51490.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s much better to give it free"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 51490.0,
      "end_time": 57460.0,
      "text": "as basic, unconditional, for everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 57460.0,
      "end_time": 58830.0,
      "text": "It does not depend"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 58830.0,
      "end_time": 62200.0,
      "text": "on what you are doing, how much you are earning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 62200.0,
      "end_time": 66280.0,
      "text": "its not dependent on if you are working or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 66280.0,
      "end_time": 70240.0,
      "text": "employed or not employed, living alone or living in the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 70240.0,
      "end_time": 74760.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just focused on the individual, focused on the human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 74760.0,
      "end_time": 78600.0,
      "text": "not circumstances, not functions."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 78600.0,
      "end_time": 84182.0,
      "text": "And that, I guess, is a necessary basis for the challenges of work we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 84182.0,
      "end_time": 86490.0,
      "text": "and the challenges in the world we live in now."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 86490.0,
      "end_time": 89080.0,
      "text": "HF: You&#39;ve been very successful with the media hype,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 89080.0,
      "end_time": 94040.0,
      "text": "you just recently set the Guinness Book World Record for the largest poster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 94040.0,
      "end_time": 98600.0,
      "text": "you dropped 400,000 Swiss francs in the square in Bern."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 98600.0,
      "end_time": 103050.0,
      "text": "E.S.: It&#39; was eight million, to represent 8 million residents in Switzerland,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 103050.0,
      "end_time": 107760.0,
      "text": "and there was about 50 tons of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 107760.0,
      "end_time": 110000.0,
      "text": "It was a golden mountain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 110000.0,
      "end_time": 112940.0,
      "text": "and it was to show that the money is there."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 112940.0,
      "end_time": 114440.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not about the money:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 114440.0,
      "end_time": 121240.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s about the unconditional, it&#39;s about abolishing ideologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 121240.0,
      "end_time": 125440.0,
      "text": "and to make a carpet for the people, a carpet for life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 125440.0,
      "end_time": 128990.0,
      "text": "[a symbol] that we can all [afford to] spend up to this amount."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 128990.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133360.0,
      "text": "H.F.: My favorite picture from that is the man vacuuming up the money"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 133360.0,
      "end_time": 137687.0,
      "text": "E.S.: Yes, again, it was not for free."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 137687.0,
      "end_time": 140560.0,
      "text": "it had to come back to the National Bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 140560.0,
      "end_time": 145300.0,
      "text": "H.F.: Do you have any figures for us about how many people are for it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 145300.0,
      "end_time": 146212.0,
      "text": "E.S.: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 146212.0,
      "end_time": 149420.0,
      "text": "Everybody is for it, in the whole world. But they don&#39;t know it yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 149420.0,
      "end_time": 150430.0,
      "text": "And.."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 150430.0,
      "end_time": 152200.0,
      "text": "(Laughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 152200.0,
      "end_time": 157670.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 157670.0,
      "end_time": 159080.0,
      "text": "H.F. How many people want it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 159080.0,
      "end_time": 161360.0,
      "text": "How many people would work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 161360.0,
      "end_time": 162690.0,
      "text": "How many people wouldn&#39;t.."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 162690.0,
      "end_time": 164800.0,
      "text": "E.S.: Ah, OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 164800.0,
      "end_time": 169400.0,
      "text": "That is really a question, and we also wanted to know that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 169400.0,
      "end_time": 173560.0,
      "text": "and so we did a survey, last December in Switzerland."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 173560.0,
      "end_time": 177040.0,
      "text": "There are many [surveys] in other countries, and many pilot projects:"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 177040.0,
      "end_time": 181210.0,
      "text": "but the result of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 181210.0,
      "end_time": 185450.0,
      "text": "was that two percent of the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 185450.0,
      "end_time": 187310.0,
      "text": "will quit their job."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 187310.0,
      "end_time": 189560.0,
      "text": "So, thanks God, it&#39;s good for them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 189560.0,
      "end_time": 192690.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t stand in their factory or in their company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 192690.0,
      "end_time": 195250.0,
      "text": "and make something bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 195250.0,
      "end_time": 200150.0,
      "text": "And eight percent will think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 200150.0,
      "end_time": 203960.0,
      "text": "So at least ten percent of the people will quit the job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 203960.0,
      "end_time": 205440.0,
      "text": "or think about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 205440.0,
      "end_time": 208280.0,
      "text": "and that does not mean they won&#39;t work oo anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 208280.0,
      "end_time": 210440.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll work on other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 210440.0,
      "end_time": 214720.0,
      "text": "And all the rest, 90 percent, want to continue working."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 214720.0,
      "end_time": 216080.0,
      "text": "And ask yourself:"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 216080.0,
      "end_time": 221390.0,
      "text": "will I stop working if my basic needs are taken care of?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 221390.0,
      "end_time": 224760.0,
      "text": "So, not you yourself, but it&#39;s always the others."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 224760.0,
      "end_time": 228800.0,
      "text": "More than 50 percent there said they want to have more time"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 228800.0,
      "end_time": 232320.0,
      "text": "for the children, for families, for social things."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 232320.0,
      "end_time": 238000.0,
      "text": "50 percent of the people said they want to have more time to study."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 238000.0,
      "end_time": 240160.0,
      "text": "And 40 percent of the people said"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 240160.0,
      "end_time": 244800.0,
      "text": "they want to have more time for free working, voluntary work."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 244800.0,
      "end_time": 249440.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s a demand by everybody to do something good for others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 249440.0,
      "end_time": 251560.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the reason to work:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 251560.0,
      "end_time": 255640.0,
      "text": "to have a responsibility, to do something good for others."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 255640.0,
      "end_time": 260959.0,
      "text": "And 13 percent said they want to change their job."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 260959.0,
      "end_time": 267880.0,
      "text": "22 percent said, they wanted to become a freelancer, self-employed."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 267880.0,
      "end_time": 271140.0,
      "text": "H.F: You mentioned jobs that people don&#39;t want to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 271140.0,
      "end_time": 274920.0,
      "text": "What does this mean for people doing the dirty work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 274920.0,
      "end_time": 276640.0,
      "text": "E.S.: An unconditional basic income?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 276640.0,
      "end_time": 277520.0,
      "text": "H.F: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 277520.0,
      "end_time": 279580.0,
      "text": "E.S. They can say no."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 279580.0,
      "end_time": 282820.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the first, and that&#39;s brilliant."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 282820.0,
      "end_time": 287240.0,
      "text": "You see, freedom is not always about being able to do what you want"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 287240.0,
      "end_time": 291920.0,
      "text": "but [also being able to] know what you really don&#39;t want to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 291920.0,
      "end_time": 296320.0,
      "text": "You cannot be forced to do anything or everything for money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 296320.0,
      "end_time": 297880.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s a brilliant thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 297880.0,
      "end_time": 301890.0,
      "text": "And the question, who cleans the toilets or who would do this work"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 301890.0,
      "end_time": 305770.0,
      "text": "what especially we both don&#39;t want to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 305770.0,
      "end_time": 307560.0,
      "text": "But the others, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 307560.0,
      "end_time": 310480.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s an old thought of the time of slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 310480.0,
      "end_time": 315560.0,
      "text": "the others have to do the work I don&#39;t want to do but it has to be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 315560.0,
      "end_time": 318160.0,
      "text": "So think of it, be a bit creative:"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 318160.0,
      "end_time": 319960.0,
      "text": "You have to pay it better!"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 319960.0,
      "end_time": 323030.0,
      "text": "If this work is necessary and its valuable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 323030.0,
      "end_time": 324740.0,
      "text": "it has to be appreciated."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 324740.0,
      "end_time": 326450.0,
      "text": "An unconditional basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 326450.0,
      "end_time": 331480.0,
      "text": "creates a huge incentive to create better work conditions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 331480.0,
      "end_time": 334720.0,
      "text": "more appreciation, more equal &quot;eye-level&quot;."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 334720.0,
      "end_time": 338280.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not so easily not to listen to the other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 338280.0,
      "end_time": 342480.0,
      "text": "not to be aware, not to care to the others."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 342480.0,
      "end_time": 345200.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s a more equal floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 345200.0,
      "end_time": 346920.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an equal flow in society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 346920.0,
      "end_time": 350040.0,
      "text": "and that means a lot by better work conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 350040.0,
      "end_time": 354930.0,
      "text": "and, as I say at least, why not pay this better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 354930.0,
      "end_time": 356280.0,
      "text": "H.F.: This all sounds great."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 356280.0,
      "end_time": 359120.0,
      "text": "But - everybody I&#39;ve asked, they all love the idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 359120.0,
      "end_time": 361580.0,
      "text": "but then they don&#39;t know how it&#39;s going to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 361580.0,
      "end_time": 365070.0,
      "text": "So what do you say to the skeptics?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 365070.0,
      "end_time": 367200.0,
      "text": "E.S.: Yeah, precisely, what I want to say is"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 367200.0,
      "end_time": 372880.0,
      "text": "you have to start the campaign, the idea, the discussion."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 372880.0,
      "end_time": 375800.0,
      "text": "Everybody is invited, we will create it together."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 375800.0,
      "end_time": 379770.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a fixed and finished model and just a calculation."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 379770.0,
      "end_time": 381000.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the first point:"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 381000.0,
      "end_time": 385400.0,
      "text": "to believe, to trust in what we are thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 385400.0,
      "end_time": 386560.0,
      "text": "and that we can do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 386560.0,
      "end_time": 389120.0,
      "text": "And then it&#39;s for me, related to direct democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 389120.0,
      "end_time": 392000.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lack in the world of the role of democracy:"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 392000.0,
      "end_time": 393960.0,
      "text": "we have to renew it."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 393960.0,
      "end_time": 397520.0,
      "text": "And then, how does it work - financially, for example -"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 397520.0,
      "end_time": 399600.0,
      "text": "is that you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 399600.0,
      "end_time": 403450.0,
      "text": "if there&#39;s an unconditional basic floor for everybody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 403450.0,
      "end_time": 408460.0,
      "text": "then wages can decrease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 408460.0,
      "end_time": 410880.0,
      "text": "about the [basic income&#39;s] amount."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 410880.0,
      "end_time": 413080.0,
      "text": "So wages and all other incomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 413080.0,
      "end_time": 415630.0,
      "text": "do no longer have the task to [fund] livelihood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 415630.0,
      "end_time": 420160.0,
      "text": "they no longer have this task to ensure existence."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 420160.0,
      "end_time": 424180.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s taken over by an unconditional basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 424180.0,
      "end_time": 425770.0,
      "text": "we give each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 425770.0,
      "end_time": 429590.0,
      "text": "And by this, when wages fall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 429590.0,
      "end_time": 432840.0,
      "text": "salaries in the public sector and the private sector,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 432840.0,
      "end_time": 437600.0,
      "text": "also social benefits securities can decrease about this amount."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 437600.0,
      "end_time": 439760.0,
      "text": "Then costs of labor decrease."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 439760.0,
      "end_time": 441960.0,
      "text": "Then costs of production decrease."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 441960.0,
      "end_time": 445074.0,
      "text": "And then for example, if you have a price for this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 445074.0,
      "end_time": 447730.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know what this is, maybe three francs?"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 447730.0,
      "end_time": 453030.0,
      "text": "And because of lower costs in the other incomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 453030.0,
      "end_time": 455940.0,
      "text": "- because they can decrease about this amount"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 455940.0,
      "end_time": 458670.0,
      "text": "of an unconditional basic income that everybody has -"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 458670.0,
      "end_time": 462600.0,
      "text": "the cost will fall, and they fall about what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 462600.0,
      "end_time": 467830.0,
      "text": "About that amount that&#39;s no longer included, contained,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 467830.0,
      "end_time": 469280.0,
      "text": "in the existing incomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 469280.0,
      "end_time": 471480.0,
      "text": "And once this part becomes free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 471480.0,
      "end_time": 476000.0,
      "text": "the room it makes in the former price structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 476000.0,
      "end_time": 479400.0,
      "text": "goes to finance the unconditional basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 479400.0,
      "end_time": 482580.0,
      "text": "in the same way it finances today&#39;s incomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 482580.0,
      "end_time": 486320.0,
      "text": "so you know every income, all incomes are financed by the prices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 486320.0,
      "end_time": 489280.0,
      "text": "and it will become a proportion in the prices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 489280.0,
      "end_time": 491280.0,
      "text": "for the unconditional basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 491280.0,
      "end_time": 496840.0,
      "text": "and a smaller proportion for the other existing incomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 496840.0,
      "end_time": 499600.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the principle, so there are many details:"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 499600.0,
      "end_time": 501800.0,
      "text": "we have a few weeks time to discuss later."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 501800.0,
      "end_time": 503462.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s first look at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 503462.0,
      "end_time": 506530.0,
      "text": "H.F.: We&#39;ve talked about the people, we&#39;ve talked about the idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 506530.0,
      "end_time": 508386.0,
      "text": "How does the money feel about this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 508386.0,
      "end_time": 510930.0,
      "text": "E.S: The money?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 510930.0,
      "end_time": 513530.0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 513530.0,
      "end_time": 516510.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an interesting question, therefore - I went in a bank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 516510.0,
      "end_time": 518720.0,
      "text": "I wanted to know how does the money feel."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 518720.0,
      "end_time": 522489.0,
      "text": "Everybody is keen to get money."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 522489.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525360.0,
      "text": "But nobody is asking what we are doing with the money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 525360.0,
      "end_time": 526960.0,
      "text": "how awful it is for the money"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 526960.0,
      "end_time": 530110.0,
      "text": "to be misused for all these horrible things."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 530110.0,
      "end_time": 533360.0,
      "text": "And I think, for me, even if it sounds funny,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 533360.0,
      "end_time": 538520.0,
      "text": "freeing the money is a thing for artists to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 538520.0,
      "end_time": 539960.0,
      "text": "or even for bankers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 539960.0,
      "end_time": 544340.0,
      "text": "so creativity and art are in every job."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 544340.0,
      "end_time": 547200.0,
      "text": "Looking to the money, doing good with money"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 547200.0,
      "end_time": 550420.0,
      "text": "may sound a bit crazy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 550420.0,
      "end_time": 551880.0,
      "text": "but at least, why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 551880.0,
      "end_time": 554480.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a look how we create it."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 554480.0,
      "end_time": 556600.0,
      "text": "You know, we don&#39;t know how we create money"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 556600.0,
      "end_time": 559760.0,
      "text": "and we think that&#39;s a miracle, that&#39;s far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 559760.0,
      "end_time": 563720.0,
      "text": "No, it&#39;s understandable: we create money"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 563720.0,
      "end_time": 570120.0,
      "text": "by giving trust and giving the right to act on initiative to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 570120.0,
      "end_time": 572280.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the creation of money, and that means"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 572280.0,
      "end_time": 575320.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not so much a part of the economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 575320.0,
      "end_time": 580050.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s much more a democratic right."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 580050.0,
      "end_time": 583580.0,
      "text": "H.F.: Do you have any closing remarks you&#39;d like to add before we end?"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 583580.0,
      "end_time": 585780.0,
      "text": "E.S.: Yes, of course, many."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 585780.0,
      "end_time": 588000.0,
      "text": "(Laughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 588000.0,
      "end_time": 594950.0,
      "text": "We just started a little view in this ongoing movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 594950.0,
      "end_time": 600560.0,
      "text": "And what I want to say  is that it concerns everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 600560.0,
      "end_time": 604900.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not the rich for the poor, not feudalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 604900.0,
      "end_time": 609380.0,
      "text": "It is a new challenge and requirement"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 609380.0,
      "end_time": 612640.0,
      "text": "to rethink things, to be responsible."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 612640.0,
      "end_time": 617760.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s yet another one step towards more freedom and responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 617760.0,
      "end_time": 621630.0,
      "text": "as we have had in history every time."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 621630.0,
      "end_time": 624640.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not new but it is a step in history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 624640.0,
      "end_time": 628090.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s as difficult as it was to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 628090.0,
      "end_time": 630840.0,
      "text": "that we really should abolish slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 630840.0,
      "end_time": 634600.0,
      "text": "that there is such an astonishing idea as human rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 634600.0,
      "end_time": 640190.0,
      "text": "and that we do this awful thing as allow everybody to vote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 640190.0,
      "end_time": 644720.0,
      "text": "and to decide, as a society, to introduce direct democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 644720.0,
      "end_time": 646600.0,
      "text": "So when you have a look in the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 646600.0,
      "end_time": 649520.0,
      "text": "[at] what our grandfathers and grandmothers did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 649520.0,
      "end_time": 654060.0,
      "text": "you see they fought for what we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 654060.0,
      "end_time": 656680.0,
      "text": "And we have to go a step further on."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 656680.0,
      "end_time": 661060.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s the same, like introducing democracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 661060.0,
      "end_time": 664600.0,
      "text": "and the other things I mentioned."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 664600.0,
      "end_time": 668090.0,
      "text": "To take this risky step"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 668090.0,
      "end_time": 670680.0,
      "text": "to an unconditional basic income for everybody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 670680.0,
      "end_time": 675680.0,
      "text": "to give this trust in society, and to strengthen civil society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 675680.0,
      "end_time": 679280.0,
      "text": "opposed and in partnership to what&#39;s going on in the economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 679280.0,
      "end_time": 681080.0,
      "text": "but in a way, independent."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 681080.0,
      "end_time": 683220.0,
      "text": "To say, who&#39;s at the top of it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 683220.0,
      "end_time": 685920.0,
      "text": "We are, the people are, you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 685920.0,
      "end_time": 689480.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s all about you, and take this to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 689480.0,
      "end_time": 694490.0,
      "text": "To lead society and not to be lead by the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 694490.0,
      "end_time": 696900.0,
      "text": "H.F.: Well thank you Enno, it&#39;s been a pleasure."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 696900.0,
      "end_time": 698880.0,
      "text": "E.S.: It was a pleasure for me. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 698880.0,
      "end_time": 708880.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}